  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为3D赛车游戏设计一个教育系统的架构图。核心是学生数据库作为入口，然后连接到LMS门户作为游戏主模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Main指向Game。那ThreeScene渲染模块应该放在哪里？它负责实际的3D场景渲染。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ThreeScene应该由Game直接驱动，标注为\"Renderiza\"渲染关系。同时ThreeScene需要关联Car和Track这两个实体。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Game到ThreeScene的渲染箭头，以及ThreeScene到Car、Track的连接。Car和Track的数据来源是哪里？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Car从LMS门户导入，Track从学生数据库导入，都用\"Importa\"标注。这样车辆配置和赛道数据可以分开管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认：Game导入Car（LMS门户来源），Game导入Track（学生数据库来源）。接下来是游戏机制模块？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要三个Hook钩子模块：Physics物理引擎、Controls控制输入、Camera摄像机系统。都用\"Hook\"标注，表示它们是动态挂载的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这三个Hook模块的数据来源有区分吗？还是都挂在Game下面？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Physics和Controls分别来自LMS门户和内容CDN，Camera来自GradeSync成绩同步系统。这样物理和控制可以独立更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
